<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html>
    <head>

        <title>Rauhanyhdistys.fi</title>
        <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
        <%= stylesheet_link_tag "global" %>
        <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'template/css/redmond/jquery-ui-1.8.11.custom' %>
        
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/static/images/srk.ico" />


        <%= javascript_include_tag "jquery-1.5.1.min" %>
        <%= javascript_include_tag "jquery-ui-1.8.11.custom.min" %>

        <script> jQuery.noConflict(); </script>

        <%= javascript_include_tag :defaults %>

        <script type="text/javascript">
          function blind(divid) {
            jQuery('#'+divid).slideToggle("slow");
          return false;
          }
        </script>

        <script>
	jQuery(document).ready(function($) {
        //$(function() {
		$( "#tabs" ).tabs();
	});
	</script>

    </head>
    <body>
        <div id="container">
            <div id="header">

            </div>
            <div id="navigation">

            </div>

          <div id="tabs">
              <ul>
                      <li><a href="#tabs-1">Rauhanyhdistykset</a></li>
                      <li><a href="#tabs-2">International</a></li>
              </ul>
              <div id="tabs-1">
                          <!-- div id="content" -->

            <h1>Rauhanyhdistykset</h1>
            <p>Rauhanyhdistysten tehtävänä on Raamatun mukaisesti kertoa ja välittää Jumalan hyviä töitä kaikkien ihmisten kuultavaksi ja uskottavaksi. Rauhanyhdistysten järjestämät seurat, pyhäkoulut, raamattuluokat ja päiväkerhot ovat kaikille avoimia tilaisuuksia. Tervetuloa!</p>

            <div id="rauhanyhdistykset">
              <ul class="kirjaimet">
                <% @customer_index.sort.each do |letter, customers| %>

                  <li><a href="#<%= letter %>"><%= letter %></a></li>
                <% end %>
              </ul>

                <% @customer_index.sort.each do |letter, customers| %>
                <h2 id="<%= letter %>"><%= letter %></h2>
                <ul>
                  <% for customer in customers %>
                    <% if customer.ryweb_active? %>
                      <li><%= link_to customer.title, "#{customer.name}" %></li>
                    <% elsif customer.home_page? %>
                      <li class="kotisivu"><%= link_to customer.title, customer.home_page %></li>
                    <% else %>
                      <li><a href="#" onclick="return blind('<%= customer.id %>')"><%= customer.title %></a>
                      <div class="blinder" id="<%= customer.id %>" style="display:none;"><%= "#{customer.address}, #{customer.zip_code} #{customer.city}<br />#{customer.phone}" %></div>
                      </li>
                    <% end %>
                  <% end %>
                </ul>
                <% end %>
            </div>
        <!-- /div -->
              </div>
              <div id="tabs-2">
                <h1>Welcome</h1>
                  <p>The SRK, the Central Committee of Conservative Laestadian Congregations is the central organization that was established in 1906. It is the central organization of the 196 local congregations, association of peace, with the main office in Oulu.</p>

                  <p>According to the by-laws of the SRK and the associations of peace, their purpose is “to awaken and inspire Christian faith life and to promote Christian moral habits, national sobriety and stabilize a patriotic mind among our people.”</p>

                  <p>To carry out the purpose, the association does mission work domestically and abroad, does and supports child and youth work, publishes literature, newspapers, magazines and recordings. The SRK has sister organisations in Sweden and North America. In addition to these, there are association of peace in Norway, Russia and Estonia. </p>

                  <div id="rauhanyhdistykset">
                  <ul class="kirjaimet">
                    <% @international_index.sort.each do |letter, customers| %>

                      <li><a href="#<%= letter %>"><%= letter %></a></li>
                    <% end %>
                  </ul>

                    <% @international_index.sort.each do |letter, customers| %>
                    <h2 id="<%= letter %>"><%= letter %></h2>
                    <ul>
                      <% for customer in customers %>
                        <% if customer.ryweb_active? %>
                          <li><%= link_to customer.title, "#{customer.name}" %></li>
                        <% elsif customer.home_page? %>
                          <li class="kotisivu"><%= link_to customer.title, customer.home_page %></li>
                        <% else %>
                          <li><a href="#" onclick="return blind('<%= customer.id %>')"><%= customer.title %></a>
                          <div class="blinder" id="<%= customer.id %>" style="display:none;"><%= "#{customer.address}, #{customer.zip_code} #{customer.city}<br />#{customer.phone}" %></div>
                          </li>
                        <% end %>
                      <% end %>
                    </ul>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
              </div>
          </div>

            <div id="footer">
                &copy; 2008 SRK
            </div>
      </div>
    </body>
</html>

